amila-cabello-c-xoxo-album-review-3768433">《C,OXO》。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glorilla">GloRilla</a>和 Rauw Alejandro 也将加入他们的行列。</p><p>该仪式原定于 9 月 10 日在纽约举行，但 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mtv-vmas-postponed-due-to-trump-vs-harris-debate-3783163">现在改为 9 月 11 日举行，</a>以避免与总统辩论发生冲突，这将是候选人<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡马拉·哈里斯</a>首次面对面。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">肯定 – 2024 年<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/VMAs?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#VMA</a>的第一批表演者已准备好启动<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2728.png" alt="✨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f680.png" alt="🚀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/Camila_Cabello?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@卡米拉_卡贝洛</a><br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/ChappellRoan?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@ChappellRoan</a> <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/GloTheofficial?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@GloTheofficial</a> <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/rauwalejandro?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@rauwalejandro</a> <br /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a4.png" alt="🎤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/SabrinaAnnLynn?ref_src=twsrc%5